         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">19/9/61 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have much pleasure in informing you that the honorable the Chief Secretary has been pleased to approve of my recommendation, that the V. G. M. I. Society ¶ Victorian Gardeners' Mu...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.09.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Harris</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 12521 Victorian Horticultural Society records, Box 3401, p. 109, La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also J. Harris to M, 17 September 1861.</p>
               </note>19/9/61</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have much pleasure in informing you that the honorable the Chief Secretary has been pleased to approve of my recommendation, that the V. G. M. I. Society<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Victorian Gardeners' Mutual Improvement Society, Melbourne.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>may avail itself of the Botanic Gardens, for holding their intended Spring Exhibition, &amp; that the customary entrance fee may be raised at the garden gates on the occasion, provided that the Society will<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not enforce such contributions<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from those persons who may be unwilling to give up the general privilege of the public, to have free access to the gardens. I beg to add that the Society will find me most ready to render such assistance as may be within my power, for the furtherance of the Exhibition —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedt</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">to J. Harris, Hon. Sec.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of the V. G. M. I. S.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to J. Harris, 27 September 1861.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
